{"tid":2258002,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯同愛字頭場波不如改做mma，一邊派兩件出黎打？","createTime":"2020-10-25T16:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T19:51:53.000Z","uid":159523,"like":33,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"81dbc2032b0dfc85a511100987b276ddaaacb6cc","tid":2258002,"uid":159523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T16:11:46.000Z","msg":"首先係曼聯，我建議派出普巴同埋麥龜<br />\n<br />\n有睇開曼聯都知，呢兩位選手雖然係足球員，但係球場上面都不時顯露佢地係巴西柔術同桑博方面既鎖技功力，估計以地面戰見長<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s50TFvX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs50TFvX.gif&h=faa4405b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6RcbCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6RcbCD.jpg&h=a838839f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於利市一哥，我建議派出碧福特同迪尼，呢兩位雖然地面技戰力一般，但係擅長下三路功課，專攻low kick，可以對對手站架做成好大既破壞力，連熱刺拳王阿里都比碧福特打到節節敗退過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HL1PdRL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHL1PdRL.gif&h=64134910&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Pv4NbM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Pv4NbM.jpg&h=60fbfcf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於裁判，可以直接邀請尋日車曼大戰既ref 艾堅遜<br />\n<br />\n與其睇兩隊係場上陰陰濕濕，不如開宗明義打mma，好睇過兩隊波係到妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提醒翻龜隊長，mma入面撩陰腿係犯規<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5Q040b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5Q040b.jpg&h=a4c04e8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b19d0f27b54ab5d80c5ce333f89f427eb06b662e","tid":2258002,"uid":70753,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T16:26:10.000Z","msg":"熱刺都想參戰<br />\n<br />\n有咩人選"},{"pid":"aca9adfaf8d99b4606e1c36d26aecec7a8623ceb","tid":2258002,"uid":103947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"應該幾好睇"},{"pid":"b4261c37019c16081e9f23908ade302262c25774","tid":2258002,"uid":381575,"like